    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="man_ej.00118_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Oakenholt Hall</name> 
                    <name type="place"><choice>
                        <abbr>nr</abbr>
                        <expan>near</expan>
                    </choice> Flint: England</name>
                    <date when="1880-07-02">2<hi rend="superscript">nd</hi> July 1880</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Walt Whitman</salute></opener>

            <p>I am very grateful for your kindness in sending me so many interesting papers from
                time to time.<ptr target="n3019"/> The article on Emerson has touched me very nearly. It is great and
                good&#8212;</p>

            <p>My object in writing now is merely to thank you for your thoughtfulness &amp; to call
                your attention to my change of address.</p>

            <closer>
                <salute>With affection &amp; respect</salute>
                <signed><hi rend="underline">Herbert J. Bathgate</hi></signed>
            </closer>
           <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="man_ej.00119_large.jpg" type="verso"/> 
        </body>
